description: An exit poll for state TV shows a huge victory for Alexander Lukashenko but opposition cries foul.
title: Belarus election: President Lukashenko set to claim landslide win
title_page: Belarus election: President Lukashenko set to claim landslide win - BBC News
maintext: In the last vote in 2015, he was declared winner with 83.5% of the vote. There were no serious challengers and election observers reported problems in the counting and tabulation of votes.
